parcel.name: SUZIE'S HAUNTED HOUSE
parcel.label: rest
parcel.description:
## SUZIE'S HAUNTED HOUSE

Thank you for visiting Suzie's Haunted House! This is completely 100% built and designed by Laugh And Belly. We hope that you enjoy your day spooked and refreshed by the creative juices overflowing from Suzie's big brain.

Find Suzie for collaborations or commissions on Twitter: @LaughAndBelly 

Or, check out all her relevant links at https://laughandbelly.com

collectible.name: Singapore Sling
collectible.author: 0x5696a8ba76ff5c6f6e1e46c20925f5a056167a2b
collectible.description:
First crafted at the Long Bar in the Raffles Hotel in Singapore in the early 1900s, the Singapore Sling is known for its bright pink-orange hue and foamy fruit punch cap. The drink combines gin, cherry brandy, and citrus juices for a sweet treat.

Editions: 88/88

Made by @LaughAndBelly on 2nd December 2021

-------------

Ingredients:

» 2 tablespoons unsweetened pineapple juice

» 1 ½ tablespoons (3/4 ounce) gin

» 1 tablespoon fresh lime juice

» 1 ½ teaspoons (1/4 ounce) orange liqueur (such as Grand Marnier)

» 1 ½ teaspoons (1/4 ounce) cherry liqueur (such as Heering)

» 1 ½ teaspoons (1/4 ounce) herbal liqueur (such as Bénédictine)

» 1 dash of homemade peach-vanilla bitters

» ¼ cup club soda

» Garnishes: Orange slices, Maraschino cherries

collectible.name: Mama's Magic Float
collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f
collectible.description: This drink looks like strawberry and grape - but it's magic, so it tastes like your favorite flavor. In Bitpixi's case, this is chocolate.. and it makes you fly! collectible.name: Skateboard #1
collectible.author: 0x5696a8ba76ff5c6f6e1e46c20925f5a056167a2b
collectible.description:
The OG 100% Maple Wood Pro Skateboard

Built by Suzie (@LaughAndBelly)

Only 3 editions of this skateboard will be available in the metaverse.

------------

Details/Specifications:

This is a 9-ply maple wood cold-pressed into 32x8-inch skateboard deck. The skateboard can support a maximum weight of 272.3 lbs (123.5 kg) with regard to thrust, speed, and ease of maneuver. It also has a medium concave that makes it ideal for any tricks.

It also comes with a SUZIE! bubble-free black griptape.

The trucks are made of long-lasting 356 T6 Aluminum hanger and baseplate, with unmatched grindabillity and kingpin clearance that helps with less wheel bite and
precision turning with Supersooz bushings.

The 53mm 99 Duro Formula Four Urethane wheels feature a smooth surface and are excellent for street or skateparks.
